cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is about improving performance on text classification tasks using data augmentation techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses neural networks, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves information retrieval (IR) tasks, which could place it in cs.IR. Finally, the paper discusses the use of smaller datasets, which could suggest it belongs to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
